# Minimize the Podman build context. The Containerfile COPYs only the
# five paths below; everything else (.git, per-agent project dirs
# .claude/.gemini/.codex, host caches, etc.) would otherwise be
# streamed to the build daemon as dead weight.
#
# `**` matches the entire tree; `!` re-includes specific files.
# Parent directories of re-included files are implicitly kept.
**
!Containerfile
!lib/log.sh
!bin/enable-dnf.sh
!bin/setup-tools.sh
!config/sudoers-enable-dnf.tmpl
